                      <div className="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Stage 7: Hal Finney</div>
                      <div className="text-sm font-semibold mb-2" style={{ color: '#9d4edd' }}>Release Schedule Vote</div>
                      <div className="text-sm mb-2" style={{ color: '#ccc' }}>
                        First Governance votes on token release schedule mechanics, establishing the repeatable process for how tokens enter circulation. This democratic decision ensures release schedule reflects community consensus rather than centralized control.
                      </div>
                      <div className="text-xs" style={{ color: '#888' }}>Dependency: Paine +⅓ constitutional consensus complete</div>
                    </div>
                    
