                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 className="font-semibold mb-2" style={{ color: '#20b2aa' }}>Monetary System</h4>
                <div className="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <div className="flex justify-between gap-4"><span style={{ color: '#ccc' }}>QuickBooks Integration</span><span style={{ color: '#20b2aa' }}>50% (Enables Locke)</span></div>
                  <div className="flex justify-between gap-4"><span style={{ color: '#ccc' }}>STORE Monetary System programmable in BitGo</span><span style={{ color: '#20b2aa' }}>50% (Enables Locke)</span></div>
                  <div className="flex justify-between gap-4"><span style={{ color: '#ccc' }}>Second Treasury Integration</span><span style={{ color: '#20b2aa' }}>50% (Enables Paine)</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 className="font-semibold mb-2" style={{ color: '#20b2aa' }}>Economies</h4>
                <div className="text-sm" style={{ color: '#ccc' }}>2-3 economies operational by December 2025-January 2026 (50% complete) • 11 total designed • Enables Paine constitutional infrastructure</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 className="font-semibold mb-2" style={{ color: '#20b2aa' }}>AI Governance</h4>
