                    <tr>
                      <td className="py-3 px-2 align-top font-semibold">Economic (5)</td>
                      <td className="py-3 px-2">First Treasury ($28.03M), STORE Monetary System (3% cap), Washington Consensus (1:1:1), TREASURIES (3 terms, 3.55-4.44% APY), STORE AI Oracle (498 endpoints)</td>
                      <td className="py-3 px-2 align-top">Operational 2017-2025</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td className="py-3 px-2 align-top font-semibold">Developer Tools (7)</td>
                      <td className="py-3 px-2">STORE Explorer, STORE Pay (14 currencies), STORE Account (50%), STORE Send (25%), API Docs IDOX (50%), SDKs, STORE NFT Publisher (60-70%), STORE Cloud Pay-on-Demand (33%)</td>
